<subSubSection id="20BC6569FFD529797079E20B3A50F9B4" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="681936E2FFD529797079E20B3A50F9B4" blockId="2.[136,1059,1394,1579]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">
One ♂ (box 11) in the collection as 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD5297971EDE20B39D6FA34" authority="(Serville, 1839)" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" class="Insecta" family="Thespidae" genus="Thesprotia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="infumata">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD5297971EDE20B3900FA34" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">Thesprotia infumata</emphasis>
(Serville, 1839)
</taxonomicName>
is almost certainly a 
<typeStatus id="B71D8840FFD52979708FE2EC3B16FA33" box="[722,805,1428,1452]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">syntype</typeStatus>
. This specimen, unfortunately rather damaged, carries three handwritten labels: &quot;♂ Amer. meri. coll. Jurine&quot;, &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797364E2AB3A2BFA74" authorityName="Saussure" authorityYear="1869" box="[313,536,1491,1515]" class="Insecta" family="Thespidae" genus="Thesprotia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="filiformis">Thesprotia filiformis</taxonomicName>
&quot; (green paper) and &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD5297970A6E2AB3C11FA74" authority="(Serv.)" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" box="[763,1058,1491,1515]" class="Insecta" family="Thespidae" genus="Thesprotia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="infumata">Thesprotia infumata (Serv.)</taxonomicName>
det. Beier&quot;. This species name is now considered a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797289E16B3A6FF9B4" authority="(Serville, 1839)" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" box="[212,604,1555,1579]" class="Insecta" family="Thespidae" genus="Thesprotia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="infumata">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797289E16B399EF9B4" box="[212,429,1555,1579]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">Thesprotia infumata</emphasis>
(Serville, 1839)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
